name: Ganarea
worshippers: Myconids and other fungus creatures. People who are diseased often beg Ganarea for mercy, offering him gifts and sacrifices.
weapon: A cloud of noxious gas or spores
tenets: Spread everywhere, leave nothing untouched. Infect everything.
parents: 3rd Generation, born of Sylvan and Area
lore: Allied themselves with Asmodeus and Malik during the gods war, wanted to leave all mortals infected with his presence.
